{
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "──3ヶ月後。\n整体院は地域密着型の健全な整体院として定着していた。"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "",
      "playSE": "door_chime"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_happysmile",
      "text": "先生、こんにちは！",
      "voiceFile": "ending_trust_max_001"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "やあ、ナナちゃん。今週もよく来たね。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_smile",
      "text": "はい。先生に会いに来ました。",
      "voiceFile": "ending_trust_max_002"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "今日は施術の予約じゃなかったよね？"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_nervoussmile",
      "text": "…はい。えへへ…ちょっとお話したくて…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_trust_max_003"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（すっかり打ち解けたな…）"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_openmouth",
      "text": "あの…学校でこんなことがあって…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_trust_max_004"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "うんうん。"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "ナナちゃんは最近の学校生活のことを楽しそうに話し始めた。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_smile_openmouth",
      "text": "それで、友達が…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_trust_max_005"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "へぇ、それは良かったね。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_closemouth",
      "text": "あと…最近ちょっと悩んでることがあって…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_trust_max_006"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "どんなこと？"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_closeeyes_closemouth",
      "text": "進路のこととか…将来のこととか…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_trust_max_007"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "そっか。色々考える時期だよね。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_openmouth",
      "text": "こういうこと…誰に相談すればいいか分からなくて…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_trust_max_008"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "俺でよければ、いつでも相談に乗るよ。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_smile",
      "text": "…ありがとうございます。",
      "voiceFile": "ending_trust_max_009"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_nervoussmile",
      "text": "先生って…お父さんみたいで…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_trust_max_010"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "お、お父さん？"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_openmouth",
      "text": "あ、いえ…それは失礼ですよね。えっと…お兄ちゃん…みたいな…？",
      "voiceFile": "ending_trust_max_011"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "ははは、どっちでも大丈夫だよ。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_happysmile",
      "text": "とにかく…すごく頼りになるんです。",
      "voiceFile": "ending_trust_max_012"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_smile",
      "text": "いてくれるだけで…安心できるというか…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_trust_max_013"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "そう言ってもらえて嬉しいよ。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_happysmile",
      "text": "はい。先生がいてくれるから、頑張れます。",
      "voiceFile": "ending_trust_max_014"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（いい子に育ったな…）"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_smile",
      "text": "あの…先生。",
      "voiceFile": "ending_trust_max_015"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "ん？"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_happysmile",
      "text": "私…先生と出会えて、本当によかったです。",
      "voiceFile": "ending_trust_max_016"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "blush_happysmile",
      "text": "施術だけじゃなくて…家族みたいに…やさしく接してくれて…",
      "voiceFile": "ending_trust_max_017"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "俺の方こそ。ナナちゃんに会えて嬉しかったよ。"
    },
    {
      "character": "nana",
      "expression": "normal_happysmile",
      "text": "これからも…ずっと、よろしくお願いします。",
      "voiceFile": "ending_trust_max_018"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "ああ、こちらこそ。"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "ナナちゃんは、施術を受けるためだけでなく、近況報告や悩み相談のためにも整体院を訪れるようになった。"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "それは施術師と患者という関係を超えた、家族のような絆だった。"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "【TRUST MAX END - 信頼の絆】",
      "triggerEnding": "trust_max"
    }
  ]
}